#LincolnCenter in New York City.. Empty and quiet streets.. NYC is absolutely beautiful. Such a fast pace and exciting city to visit. Everyone is always in such a rush to get somewhere and streets are crowded but seeing empty streets like this, did I have the real NYC experience? 🤣🤣 .
